Quite challenging. In the end you can reproduce this with

     $ cd AllelicImbalance/data
     $ R --vanilla

and then

     env = new.env()
     load("ASEset.rdata", env)
     get("ASEset", env)

The problem is with BiocParallel, and a work-around is in place in version 
