>
>                                                              It does
>         take the
>                  coverage
>                           into account;
>                                                     specifically to exclude
>                                                              the introns
>                                                              from
>         coverage. I think
>                           there's also an
>                                    option
>                                                     to exclude
>                                                     deletions.
